    "revelation": "Every sound in the dub tradition starts with restraint and earns its echo.",
    "diagnosis": "Wax Cut establishes the foundation tone — the pre-echo signal that gives all other OVERDUB presets their ground. Without a compelling dry tone, the reverb has nothing to multiply."
